Validation of branching ratios for the D mesons

With these scripts one can verify the branching ratios of certain decay modes and compare them to PDG values

USAGE:

1. RUN ONE VALIDATION JOB (EvtGenValidate_D.py)
   Provide an input file and output file name for validating the data.
   - basf2 EvtGenValidate_D.py input.root output.root


2. RUN MULTIPLE SKIM JOBS (EvtGenValidate_DJobs.py)
   Provide an input directory for validating the data. Root files are produced in a new rootFiles/ directory.
   - basf2 EvtGenValidate_DJobs.py inputDir

3. CREATE BRANCHING RATIO TABLES (EvtGenValidate_BrTables.C)
   - root -l EvtGenValidate_BrTable.C   # Here you are asked for the input file name and the table output format